{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8ec8a910-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s286jj"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"286jj"},"text":"§ 286jj.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Partial guarantees in connection with debt reduction for borrower countries","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of the Treasury shall instruct the United States Executive Director of the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development to initiate discussions with other directors of such bank and to propose that such bank establish criteria under which such bank would provide partial guarantees on debt service payments by borrower countries to private creditors when such guarantees would serve a catalytic role in facilitating final agreement on financing packages which involve significant debt reduction.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8ec8a911-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/461/tV/s555"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–461, title V, § 555","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/2268-36"},"text":"102 Stat. 2268–36","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8ec8a912-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8ec8a913-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id8ec8a914-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is based on section 5 of H.R. 4645, One Hundredth Congress, as reported ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-09-28"},"text":"Sept. 28, 1988","children":[],"tail":", and enacted into law by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/461"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–461","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was not enacted as part of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1945-07-31/ch339"},"text":"act July 31, 1945, ch. 339","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/59/512"},"text":"59 Stat. 512","children":[],"tail":", known as the Bretton Woods Agreements Act, which comprises this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
